about.description:
This package contains the static libraries and header files needed for
developing gtkmm applications.
about.summary: (CDT) Headers for developing programs that will use gtkmm24.

name: gtkmm24-devel-cos6-x86_64
raw_recipe:
package:
  name: gtkmm24-devel-cos6-x86_64
  version: 2.18.2

source:
  - url: http://mirror.centos.org/centos/6.10/os/x86_64/Packages/gtkmm24-devel-2.18.2-1.el6.x86_64.rpm
    sha256: 198d4475254ff9e36dc901164c677c97c74526e545cadbe8e6c0609d8c0c116c
    no_hoist: true
    folder: binary
  # - url: http://vault.centos.org/6.10/os/Source/SPackages/gtkmm24-2.18.2-1.el6.src.rpm
  #   no_hoist: true
  #   folder: source

build:
  number: {{ cdt_build_number }}
  noarch: generic
  binary_relocation: false
  detect_binary_files_with_prefix: false
  missing_dso_whitelist:
    - '*'

requirements:
  build:
    - gtkmm24-cos6-x86_64 ==2.18.2 *_{{ cdt_build_number }}
  host:
    - gtkmm24-cos6-x86_64 ==2.18.2 *_{{ cdt_build_number }}
  run:
    - gtkmm24-cos6-x86_64 ==2.18.2 *_{{ cdt_build_number }}
  run_constrained:
    - sysroot_linux-64 ==99999999999

test:
  commands:
    - echo "it installs!"

about:
  home: http://gtkmm.sourceforge.net/
  license: LGPL-2.0-or-later
  license_family: LGPL
  license_file:
    - gtkmm-license
    - gtkmm-tools-license
  summary: (CDT) Headers for developing programs that will use gtkmm24.
  description: |
    This package contains the static libraries and header files needed for
    developing gtkmm applications.

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/help-cdts
